you get with your Delta tables in there.

00:51:01.884 --> 00:51:03.884
And it's been growing extremely quickly.

00:51:05.384 --> 00:51:07.423
We now have 5,000 monthly active customers and if you look at

00:51:07.423 --> 00:51:10.143
the graph of queries on lake house federation, it's still

00:51:10.143 --> 00:51:12.143
growing exponentially.

00:51:13.564 --> 00:51:15.564
So it's a really cool thing to be able to

00:51:16.624 --> 00:51:18.624
have all of your data in one place and

00:51:19.704 --> 00:51:21.704
have all of your stuff in one system, it's just not the case.

00:51:22.963 --> 00:51:24.963
And actually work with it together.

00:51:26.024 --> 00:51:28.064
And another really cool thing that we're announcing is lake

00:51:28.064 --> 00:51:30.064
house federation for Apache Hive and Glue.

00:51:32.143 --> 00:51:34.404
So if you've got an existing Hive meta store or Glue, you've

