As you mentioned, metrics enhance

01:08:12.044 --> 01:08:14.044
business users' ability to ask questions,

01:08:14.044 --> 01:08:16.044
understand their organization's data,

01:08:16.044 --> 01:08:18.044
and ultimately make better decisions.

01:08:18.044 --> 01:08:20.044
Rather than sifting through all of the

01:08:20.044 --> 01:08:22.044
data, certified business metrics can be

01:08:22.044 --> 01:08:24.044
governed, discovered, and queried

01:08:24.044 --> 01:08:26.044
efficiently through Unity Catalog.

