01:17:55.587 --> 01:17:57.686
So two things really distinguish Databricks cleanrooms from

01:17:57.686 --> 01:17:59.686
other cleanroom solutions out there.

01:18:01.046 --> 01:18:03.026
The first is because you have this complete data and AI

01:18:03.026 --> 01:18:05.026
platform, you can really run any computation.

01:18:07.207 --> 01:18:09.207
It can be machine learning, SQL, Python, R

01:18:10.727 --> 01:18:12.727
and so on versus just SQL in many other cleanroom solutions.

01:18:12.727 --> 01:18:14.727
And the second is because you have a

01:18:15.787 --> 01:18:17.826
cleanroom solution, you can do cross-cloud and even cross-platform

01:18:17.826 --> 01:18:19.826
collaboration.

