There were so many challenges

01:28:46.707 --> 01:28:48.707
that we faced just a few years ago

01:28:48.707 --> 01:28:50.707
when we began our data modernization

01:28:50.707 --> 01:28:52.707
journey. Stop me

01:28:52.707 --> 01:28:54.707
if any of this sounds familiar.

