01:58:41.332 --> 01:58:43.251
step is to transform it.

01:58:43.251 --> 01:58:47.651
As it turns out, newly ingested data is almost never ready for use by the business.

01:58:47.651 --> 01:58:51.692
You have to filter it, you have to aggregate it, you have to append it and clean it.

01:58:51.692 --> 01:58:55.051
Lots of technology choices, DBT, a great open source project.

01:58:55.051 --> 01:58:58.452
You might have heard about Delta Life Tables and PySpark, Ronald was telling you how popular

01:58:58.452 --> 01:58:59.452
it is.

01:58:59.452 --> 01:59:00.651
