01:59:00.651 --> 01:59:02.411
And again, how do you monitor it?

01:59:02.411 --> 01:59:04.332
How do you maintain it?

01:59:04.332 --> 01:59:08.051
And once your data is transformed, that's really not even half the battle.

01:59:08.051 --> 01:59:12.511
You get the value out of data by actually running your production pipelines in production.

01:59:12.511 --> 01:59:16.871
I don't like waking up at 2 in the morning with an alert, so now you have to orchestrate.

01:59:16.871 --> 01:59:18.192
So you might be using Airflow.

01:59:18.192 --> 01:59:19.192
Great.

01:59:19.192 --> 01:59:21.551
