01:59:25.432 --> 01:59:28.631
And then, of course, you might have to monitor all these things in CloudWatch.

01:59:28.631 --> 01:59:34.952
This is unnecessarily complex, and this is inefficient, and it's actually very expensive.

01:59:34.952 --> 01:59:40.312
Which is why I am extremely proud to unveil what we're calling Databricks Lakeflow.

01:59:40.312 --> 01:59:52.271
This is a new product that's built on a fundamental foundation of Databricks workflows and Delta

01:59:52.271 --> 01:59:54.631
Life Tables with a little bit of magic sauce added on.

